<?xml version="1.0"?>
<html>
  <problem>
    <title> CheckPoint: Torque </title>

      <p>A square plate ABCD with a side d is acted upon by several forces of equal magnitude F as shown. Point E is the center of the square, G is the midpoint of BC, K is the midpoint of CD, and L is the midpoint of AD.</p>
      <br/>

    <img width="654" alt="BK77" src="/static/problems/MIT/rayyan/check_points/Pictures/BK77.png"/>
        <br/>

      <p>Part 1. Find the magnitude of the net torque acting on the plate with respect to the axis passing through point A perpendicular to the page.</p>

      <br/>
      <multiplechoiceresponse direction="vertical" randomize="no" type="MultipleChoice">
        <choicegroup type="MultipleChoice">
          <choice location="random" name="foil1" correct="true">
                \(Fd/2 + Fd\frac{1}{2\sqrt {2}}\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil2" correct="false">
                \(3Fd/2\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil3" correct="false">
                \(Fd/2 - Fd\frac{1}{2\sqrt {2}}\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil4" correct="false">
				\(Fd/2\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil5" correct="false">
				\(2Fd\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil6" correct="true">
				\(3Fd/2\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil7" correct="false">
				\(5Fd/2\)
          </choice>
        </choicegroup>
      </multiplechoiceresponse>


        <p>Part 2. Find the magnitude of the net torque acting on the plate with respect to the axis passing through point K perpendicular to the page.</p>

      <br/>
      <multiplechoiceresponse direction="vertical" randomize="no" type="MultipleChoice">
        <choicegroup type="MultipleChoice">
          <choice location="random" name="foil1" correct="true">
                \(Fd\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil2" correct="false">
                \(5Fd/2\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil3" correct="false">
                \(Fd/2\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil4" correct="false">
                \(3Fd/2 + Fd\sqrt {2}\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil5" correct="false">
                \(3Fd/2 - Fd\sqrt {2}\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil6" correct="false">
				\(3Fd/2\)
          </choice>
        </choicegroup>
      </multiplechoiceresponse>

        <p>Part 3. Find the magnitude of the net torque acting on the plate with respect to the axis passing through point E perpendicular to the page.</p>

      <br/>
      <multiplechoiceresponse direction="vertical" randomize="no" type="MultipleChoice">
        <choicegroup type="MultipleChoice">
          <choice location="random" name="foil1" correct="true">
                \(Fd + Fd\frac{1}{2\sqrt {2}}\) 
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil2" correct="false">
                \(Fd/2 + Fd\frac{1}{2\sqrt {2}}\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil3" correct="false">
                \(Fd - Fd\frac{1}{2\sqrt {2}}\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil4" correct="false">
                \(Fd/2 - Fd\frac{1}{2\sqrt {2}}\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil5" correct="false">
                \(2Fd + Fd\frac{1}{2\sqrt {2}}\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil6" correct="false">
				\(2Fd - Fd\frac{1}{\sqrt {2}}\)
          </choice>
        </choicegroup>
      </multiplechoiceresponse>

        <p>Part 4. Find the magnitude of the net torque acting on the plate with respect to the axis passing through point L perpendicular to the page.</p>

      <br/>
      <multiplechoiceresponse direction="vertical" randomize="no" type="MultipleChoice">
        <choicegroup type="MultipleChoice">
          <choice location="random" name="foil1" correct="true">
                \(Fd/2\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil2" correct="false">
                \(Fd/2 + Fd\frac{1}{2\sqrt {2}}\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil3" correct="false">
                \(Fd/2 - Fd\frac{1}{2\sqrt {2}}\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil4" correct="false">
                \(Fd\)
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil5" correct="false">
                \(3Fd/2\)
          </choice>
        </choicegroup>
      </multiplechoiceresponse>


        <p>Part 5. Consider the net torques acting on the plate with respect to the axes passing through A, K, E and L (see parts 1-4). Their directions, respectively, are:</p>

      <br/>
      <multiplechoiceresponse direction="vertical" randomize="yes" type="MultipleChoice">
        <choicegroup type="MultipleChoice">
          <choice location="random" name="foil1" correct="true">
                counterclockwise; counterclockwise; counterclockwise; counterclockwise 
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil2" correct="false">
                clockwise; clockwise; clockwise; clockwise
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil3" correct="false">
                counterclockwise; clockwise; counterclockwise; clockwise
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil4" correct="false">
                counterclockwise; counterclockwise; clockwise; clockwise
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil5" correct="false">
                counterclockwise; clockwise; counterclockwise; counterclockwise
          </choice>
          <choice location="random" name="foil6" correct="false">
				counterclockwise; clockwise; clockwise; counterclockwise
          </choice>
        </choicegroup>
      </multiplechoiceresponse>

    </problem>
</html>
